Installation
============

This program requires

o GTK+ 2.4.0 or higher
o GLib 2.4.0 or higher
o libxml2 2.6.0 or higher
o OpenSSL 0.9.1c or higher
o gpgme 0.4.5 or higher (option)

to be compiled.

This program is developed on Vine Linux 3.1
(Linux 2.4.x + glibc 2.3.3), so it is possible not to work correctly
on the other environment.

It is confirmed to work on the following environments:

Linux

o Vine Linux 3.1

BSD

Hmm...

Other commercial Unix

o Mac OS X 10.3 + X11 for Mac OS X + Todaifink

Others

Hmm...

Build it
========

Please make sure that gtk-devel, glib-devel, libxml2-devel, openssl-devel
and gpgme-devel (or similar) packages are installed before the compilation.

To compile and install, just type:

% ./configure
% make
% su
Password: [Enter password]
# make install

Options for configure script
============================

Please refer to ./configure --help .


If the installation of Mnid failed, check whether all the required
libraries are correctly installed. If it still failed, please send bug
report to:

NOGUCHI Shoji <noguchi@org3.net>
